fields.physical_description:
1.  original box, card printed in colours on black to show the title, maker's details, illustrations of shapes in grey and photographs of various models together with 325pcs.  Some of the details are given in different languages.  The box has opening flaps at each end and a cut away panel at the top.
2.  instructions booklet, cover printed in black , yellow and white and the photographs in colour.  The text is in 13 languages.  At the back ae details of the various pieces and the number that should be present which totals 332.  The booklet also bears the Ref. number 43010 and its own 95210.
3.  leaflet, printed in colours to show the various sets available, their reference numbers and the objects which could be made from them.
It is numbered 94299.
4.  carrying case, moulded yellow plastic; briefcase style with moulded hand grip.  The front of the box opens to reveal the space to hold the pieces.  The inside of the lid is moulded with the same marks as seen on the box.
5,6.  large tyres with heavy tread, moulded black soft vinyl; diam 3½ in 
         (8.9cm)
7,8.  mid sized tyres with heavy tread, moulded black soft vinyl, 
         diam 2 5/8in (6.7cm)
9-12.  small tyres with heavy tread, moulded black soft vinyl, diam 1¾in
         (4.5cm)
13-16.  wheels, moulded grey plastic, diam 2in (5.1cm)
17-20.  wheels, moulded grey plastic, diam 1½in (3.8cm)
21-34.  rings or circles, 8 spokes, moulded white plastic; diam 1½in  
             (3.8cm)
35-47.  semi-circular rings with bottom panel missing, 3½ spokes, moulded purple plastic, diam. 1 3/8in (3.4cm)
48-59.  near rings or circles missing one panel, 6 spokes and two ½ spokes, moulded dark blue plastic, diam 1½in (3.8cm)
60-80.  semi-circular rings, 4 spokes, moulded yellow plastic,
              diam 1½in (3.8cm)
81-102.  part circle, 3 spokes, moulded green plastic, diam 1½in (3.8)
103-129.  part circle, 2 spokes, moulded red plastic, diam 1¼in (3.2cm)
130-142.  part circle, 1 spoke, moulded light grey plastic, diam 1in (2.5)
143-169.  ladder, moulded orange plastic, Ht. 1½in (3.8cm)
170-203.  short ladder, moulded dark grey plastic, Ht. 1in (2.5cm)
204-211.  key, moulded beige plastic, Ht. 5/8in (1.6cm)
212-224.  rod, moulded grey plastic,  L. 7 5/8in (19.3cm)
225-240.  rod, moulded red plastic,  L. 5 1/8in (13cm)
241-261.  rod, moulded yellow plastic, L. 3 3/8in (8.6cm)
